# Window Rules
 
for_window [class="^.*"] border pixel 2

for_window [title=".*Mozilla Firefox.*"] border none
assign [title=".*Mozilla Firefox.*"] workspace 2.http

assign [title=".*Telegram.*"] workspace 4.msg
assign [title=".*Slack.*"] workspace 4.msg
assign [title=".*Discord.*"] workspace 4.msg
assign [title=".*Thunderbird.*"] workspace 3.mail


exec swaymsg mouse_warping container
